message.content: The paper belongs to the arXiv CS sub-category "cs.CL" (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and multimodal question answering. Other likely sub-categories could include "cs.CV" (Computer Vision) and "cs.IR" (Information Retrieval) as the paper also involves analyzing images and tables. "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence) and "cs.LG" (Machine Learning) could also be possible sub-categories as the paper involves developing a baseline model for ManyModalQA.
